      "type": "heading",
      "content": "Introduction to AkiraDocs",
      "metadata": {
        "level": 1
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "3",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "AkiraDocs is a next-generation documentation platform that combines the power of AI with an intuitive content management system. It's designed to transform your documentation workflow from months to minutes."
    },
    {
      "id": "4",
      "type": "heading",
      "content": "Why AkiraDocs?",
      "metadata": {
        "level": 2
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "5",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "Documentation is often a challenge for teams:"
    },
    {
      "id": "6",
      "type": "list",
      "content": [
        "Developers want to keep using Markdown and Git",
        "Content teams need user-friendly editors",
        "Technical writers struggle with version management",
        "Product managers deal with out-of-sync documentation",
        "Enterprise leaders need better analytics"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "listType": "unordered"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "7",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "AkiraDocs solves these challenges by providing a unified platform that brings everyone's workflow together."
    },
    {
      "id": "8",
      "type": "heading",
      "content": "Core Benefits",
      "metadata": {
        "level": 2
      }
